title: Chuck II X Futura Collaboration
description:
Legendary graffiti artist, Futura, and his son, photographer, 13th Witness sat down to discuss his brand new sneaker and our first ever #ChuckII collaboration

Music produced by Forest Pond
Additional video by Tarik Sykes
